  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/000642207ab4d9d56ea6f459262e2d48.poster.avif?t=1637687220\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/000642207ab4d9d56ea6f459262e2d48.webm?t=1637687220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/000642207ab4d9d56ea6f459262e2d48.mp4?t=1637687220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Hundreds of enemies on-screen -</strong> Defend against an ever-increasing swarm of hostile alien creatures. Hundreds upon hundreds of visible enemies marching upon your base simultaneously.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/6eb8ef787898884b0ae8d135e474de2f.poster.avif?t=1637687220\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/6eb8ef787898884b0ae8d135e474de2f.webm?t=1637687220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/6eb8ef787898884b0ae8d135e474de2f.mp4?t=1637687220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Build and upgrade towers -</strong> Choose from an assortment of towers to build that fulfill the needs of various situations. Upgrade those towers in different and unique ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/b8b3deab25c364a3a5abf13db4c18d3d.poster.avif?t=1637687220\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/b8b3deab25c364a3a5abf13db4c18d3d.webm?t=1637687220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/b8b3deab25c364a3a5abf13db4c18d3d.mp4?t=1637687220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Learn and use abilities -</strong> Acquire varied types of abilities to create unique combinations and use at crucial times to turn the tide of the battlefield.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/aa1448989aef8e540af97824b70193f8.poster.avif?t=1637687220\" width=640 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/aa1448989aef8e540af97824b70193f8.webm?t=1637687220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595090/extras/aa1448989aef8e540af97824b70193f8.mp4?t=1637687220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Randomized upgrades -</strong> Choose between three sets of upgrades every upgrade phase. Every set of upgrades consists of positive benefits for you as well as upgrades for the alien swarm. Use tactical decision-making to create wild combinations while adapting to evolving strengths of the alien menace.<br><br><strong>Campaign mode -</strong> On the run in a hostile galaxy and low on resources, play through a non-invasive story on customized scenarios for each map.<br><br><strong>Skirmish mode -</strong> Customize any map to match your own desired specifications. From which enemies are present to speed of upgrades, difficulty can be fine tuned to how you want it.",
